definitions.definition: The production of an instance , example , or specific application of a general classification, principle, theory, etc.
Something resulting from the act of instantiating ; an instance.
Creation of an instance of some class or template .

main_definition: ( uncountable ) The production of an instance , example , or specific application of a general classification, principle, theory, etc.
secondary_definitions: ( countable ) Something resulting from the act of instantiating ; an instance.
( by extension , object-oriented programming ) Creation of an instance of some class or template .
